{"tid":2423673,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"MWYO報告:港青今年失業率或見13%","createTime":"2021-02-26T05:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T10:46:23.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f31fc351c5ae543e961a9c7baed1a61c632f9d0","tid":2423673,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"MWYO青年辦公室發表《2021-22青年失業率預測分析報告》，悲觀情況下，預測港青今年第四季失業率達13%。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，20至29歲群組和整體失業率難以在今年內回到疫情前的水平。在基本情況下，預測20至29歲群組的失業率在今年第四季縱使比前一季的13%大跌至11.3%，但仍高於2019年第四季(疫情爆發前一季)的5.9%接近一倍。<br />\n<br />\n而在悲觀情況下，疫苗注射計劃出現嚴重滯後，而疫情於2022年第一季才結束，今年第四季的20至29歲群組的失業率將達13%。青年就業情況要恢復數年前水平的道路仍然漫長，亟待政府推出及時有效的紓緩措施。"},{"pid":"dfa3aa12237d6ca640921fe6440cfe065bb4fa11","tid":2423673,"uid":64576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"政府根本無諗住幫年青人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d7a3b72193ed31fb32633a27e5965c518dd00c","tid":2423673,"uid":54623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfa3aa12237d6ca640921fe6440cfe065bb4fa11","tid":2423673,"uid":64576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"政府根本無諗住幫年青人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:11:52.000Z","msg":"要幫都幫中國人先啦<br />\n邊洗理香港啲二等公民香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3c6c35319bd6b2ffdc55ab41a28296624a400f","tid":2423673,"uid":40804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"fg失到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51e0444cedbcdb02ac7c72a4c63a930b7d93e30","tid":2423673,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"dfa3aa12237d6ca640921fe6440cfe065bb4fa11","tid":2423673,"uid":64576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"政府根本無諗住幫年青人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla